<row>
<entry valign="top">Partnership</entry>
<entry valign="top"><list list-type="bulleted" id="list-00003">
<item>More expertise and managerial skills available.</item>
<item>Relatively low organizational costs.</item>
<item>Income taxed as personal income of partners.</item>
<item>Fundraising ability is enhanced by more owners.</item>
</list></entry>
<entry valign="top"><list list-type="bulleted" id="list-00004">
<item>Owners have unlimited liability; may have to cover debts of other, less financially sound partners.</item>
<item>Dissolves or must reorganize when partner dies.</item>
<item>Difficult to liquidate or terminate.</item>
<item>Potential for conflicts between partners.</item>
<item>Difficult to achieve large-scale operations.</item>
</list></entry>
